text: Bolshetenkashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baygildinsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 320 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Krasnaya Gorka, 3 km from Baygildino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Bolshetenkashevo
